title: Schlock Mercenary - Complete through March 2015 {WebComixFan}
description:
"SCHLOCK MERCENARY" Web Comic

"Schlock Mercenary" (schlockmercenary.com) by Howard Tayler follows the tribulations of a star-travelling mercenary company in a satiric, mildly dystopian 31st-century space opera setting.  It has been nominated for four Hugo Awards.

This torrent collects "Schlock Mercenary" comics, from the strip's beginning in June 2000 to the end of book 15 in March 2015.  Though the CBR files in the set correspond to the published volumes of the comic, they are NOT scans of the books; all the comics in this torrent were downloaded directly from the schlockmercenary.com Web site
